column4: 1 for a navigable index/switchboard with links to forms and reports, and forms have strong validation, selection options and linked tables when applicable; else 0.75 for a switchboard/index and forms (non-validating or non-linked-tables); else 0.75 for forms (non-validating or non-linked-tables) and three reports; else 0.65 for forms (non-validating or non-linked-tables) and reports; else 0.6 for forms (non-validating or non-linked-tables) and queries; else 0.5 for queries
